4. cs.MA (Multiagent Systems): The paper deals with multiple agents (members of the network) interacting with each other, which is a topic covered in this sub-category. 
5. cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms): While not the most likely sub-category, the paper does involve the optimization of a cost function, which could potentially fall under the scope of this sub-category.
